body:
I have tested with current `master` and have confirmed the issue still exists.

`tf.__version__` returns `0.10.0`; `tf.__git_version__` returns `v0.10.0rc0-2191-gf38886b`; running `git log` in the TF repo I just built and installed gives the the latest commit of `f38886ba307314cc0ae5b15279f5693f39c92f21` (which confirms that the `tf.__git_version__` is correct).
